    title: "7 Key Factors When Choosing Salon CRM Software",
    seoTitle: "7 Key Factors When Choosing Salon CRM Software | Swalook Guide",
    seoDescription: "A complete guide to the 7 essential factors for choosing salon CRM software — client retention, marketing automation, billing, inventory, analytics, scalability, and more. Make the right choice for your Indian salon.",
    slug: "7-key-factors-for-choosing-salon-crm-software",
    href: "/blog/7-key-factors-for-choosing-salon-crm-software",
    category: "Salon CRM & Software Guide",
    excerpt: "Selecting the right CRM for your salon is a critical business decision that impacts client retention, staff productivity, and revenue growth. This comprehensive guide walks through the 7 essential factors — from client retention features and marketing automation to scalability, pricing transparency, and team adoption — so you can make an informed choice that drives real, measurable growth for your salon business.",
    coverImage: `${IMAGE_BASE}/blog-crm-guide.svg`,
    ogImage: `${IMAGE_BASE}/blog-crm-guide.svg`,
    coverImageAlt: "7 key factors for choosing salon CRM software illustrated with icons for retention, marketing, billing, analytics, inventory, scheduling, and scalability",
    readTime: "12 min read",
    publishedAt: "2026-01-15",
