    excerpt: "Manual salon management leads to missed appointments, lost client data, and stunted growth. This in-depth article explores the real costs of operating without a CRM — from no-show losses and staff inefficiency to missed revenue opportunities — and how Swalook specifically addresses these challenges for Indian salons with measurable results.",
